[49m[38;5;10m+    194[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    195[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## General Architecture Pattern
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    196[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    197[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A healthcare care-coordination assistant decomposes into ten logical stages: enrollment and consent, longitudinal-store initialization across multiple data sources, channel entry with disclosure refresh, input safety screening with continuous emergency screening, identity-and-context loading from multiple sources, conversation handling with multi-corpus-grounded responses, output safety screening with conflict-detection and scope verification, escalation routing to the human care-management team, care-team summary reporting with consent enforcement, and audit logging with multi-source retention discipline. The cross-cutting concerns from recipes 11.1 through 11.8 carry forward; this recipe adds five new ones (multi-source longitudinal-context retrieval as architectural primitive, cross-clinician instruction-conflict detection, care-coordination-protocol library with care-management-team ownership, human care-management-team backstop with named operational ownership, multi-tenant cross-institution awareness).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    198[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    199[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    200[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ENROLLMENT + LAYERED CONSENT ──────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    201[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    202[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient enrolls via institution app, payer benefits    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    203[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    portal, or referral from a care manager]              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    204[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Documented base consent for the bot                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    205[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Layered consent for chart-context access             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    206[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Layered consent for cross-institution-exchange       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    207[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      access (HIE, QHIN, payer-side claims)                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    208[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Layered consent for caregiver access                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    209[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Layered consent for care-team summary reporting      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Each layer separately revocable                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Crisis-resource information surfaced                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Privacy posture explained in plain language          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: signed consent record per layer; enrollment    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    confirmation; initialization of longitudinal store]    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── LONGITUDINAL STORE INITIALIZATION ─────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient-bot longitudinal store, populated from         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    multiple sources per consent]                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    224[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active conditions on the problem list                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    225[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Current medications and allergies                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    226[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team roster (PCP, specialists, care manager,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      navigator, social worker, behavioral-health, home    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    228[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      health, pharmacy, etc.)                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    229[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent encounters (last 12-24 months)                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    230[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active referrals (made, scheduled, completed)        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scheduled and pending appointments                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active care plan and goals (where documented)        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent care-management touches                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Insurance posture and benefits context               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Caregiver roster (where documented and consented)    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cross-institution data summary (HIE, claims) where   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      consent permits                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Stated patient preferences                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation history (initially empty)               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: longitudinal store ready for conversations]    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── CHANNEL ENTRY WITH DISCLOSURE ─────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient-initiated entry]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - In-app chat (most common)                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - SMS (where supported, with appropriate consent)      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Web chat                                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Voice channel (where supported, with accessibility   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      considerations for the population)                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Bot-initiated entry, with care]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Event-triggered (referral made, appointment booked,  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      lab result received, hospital discharge happened)    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scheduled check-ins per patient stated preference    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-manager-requested touches                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Caregiver-initiated entry, where consented]            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Caregiver authenticates with separate identity       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Bot's surface-to-caregiver scope reflects the        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      consent the patient provided                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    265[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Disclosure refresh per session or defined cadence]     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: session_id, channel, auth context, disclosure  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    acknowledged, caller-role identified]                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    272[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    273[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    274[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── INPUT SAFETY + EMERGENCY SCREENING ────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    275[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    276[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Standard input safety primitives from recipe 11.1]     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    277[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Prompt-injection detection                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    278[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - PHI minimization                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    279[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    280[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Continuous emergency screening from recipe 11.6]       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    281[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - 911 patterns: chest pain, stroke symptoms, severe    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    282[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      bleeding, acute respiratory distress, anaphylaxis,   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    283[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      altered mental status, severe trauma                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    284[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Triggers triage-pathway response immediately         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    285[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    286[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Continuous crisis screening from recipe 11.8]          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    287[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Self-harm, suicidal ideation                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    288[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Triggers crisis-pathway response immediately         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    289[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    290[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Sensitive-disclosure detection]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    291[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Elder-abuse indicators (mandatory-reporting)         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    292[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Financial exploitation                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    293[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Intimate-partner violence                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    294[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Caregiver burden / caregiver crisis                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    295[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Severe medication side effects                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    296[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-plan-deviation patterns                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    297[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    298[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    299[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: input passes / input blocked / emergency       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    300[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    pathway triggered / crisis pathway triggered /         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    301[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    sensitive disclosure flagged for routing]              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    302[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    303[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    304[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    305[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── IDENTITY + MULTI-SOURCE CONTEXT LOADING ───────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    306[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    307[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Authenticated session]                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    308[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient or caregiver, with role identified           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    309[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    310[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Multi-source longitudinal-context retrieval]           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    311[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Institution chart context (FHIR resources)           │
