[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    524[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Durable conversation record]                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    525[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - User utterances (caller role tagged)                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    526[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Tool calls with arguments and results                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    527[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Generated bot responses                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    528[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active model and prompt versions                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    529[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active care-coordination-protocol-library version    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    530[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active conflict-detection-rule version               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    531[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Final disposition                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    532[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    533[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Multi-source retention discipline]                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    534[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-source access events logged                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    535[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-source data-use-agreement scope honored          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    536[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cross-institution-data retention sized to QHIN /     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    537[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      HIE / payer-side data-use-agreement requirements     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    538[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - HIPAA's six-year minimum baseline                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    539[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    540[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Outcome correlation as long-time-horizon commitment]   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    541[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Multi-quarter to multi-year implementation           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    542[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Owned jointly by care-management leadership,         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    543[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      operations, and data science                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    544[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    545[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Operational telemetry]                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    546[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Engagement rate by patient cohort                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    547[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Attrition rate by patient cohort                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    548[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conflict-detection rate (per-cohort)                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    549[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Escalation-to-human rate (per-cohort)                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    550[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Time-to-care-manager-pickup on escalations           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    551[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Citation-coverage rate                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    552[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Tool-call success rate per source                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    553[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Data-source freshness per integration                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    554[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-cohort metric slices (language, channel,         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    555[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      condition, age cohort, sex, social-determinant       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    556[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      flags, caregiver-mediated vs. patient-direct)        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    557[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    558[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Sampled clinical-quality review]                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    559[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Random sample plus targeted sample of conflict-      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    560[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      detection cases, escalations, and low-confidence     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    561[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      interactions                                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    562[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Reviewers (care-management leadership) tag failure   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    563[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      modes (out-of-scope, missed-conflict, false-conflict,│
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    564[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      stale-data, escalation-miss, escalation-false-       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    565[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      positive, scope-violation, citation-gap, tone-       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    566[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      failure, equity-disparity)                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    567[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-coordination-protocol-library revisions driven  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    568[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      by review findings                                   │
